      "title": "'Gas' comes out of the laughing gas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Laugh Gas Company has decided to reduce the price of a domestic gas cylinder by 1050 rupees from midnight tonight.",
        "Accordingly, the new price of a 12.5 kg cylinder will come down to 5800 rupees. Relative to this price reduction, the price of a 5 kg gas cylinder of that company will also come down."
      ],
